- It is a Platform As A Service (PAAS) with a remote platform to run & execute your backend code
- Its a automated version of ec2
- for  executing  background task only .
- automatic scale depends upon the traffic.
- pay the amount of time only the code is executed
- We can run only python, nodejs, java, Go,ruby,.net languages only.
Defination: It is serverless compute service

To use this service we need to use SDK (Software Devlopment Kit) provided by aws

AWS SDK's
It is an API which is used by developers to desire service they want.
These SDK's are used by IDE's 
i.e. Eclipse 
Visual Studio
